What you need to know:

For the first time, the elders watched a video footage of how the cut was performed on a seven-year-old girl, overpowered by five women.As the ''surgeon'' cut through the flesh with a blunt knife and a razor blade without any form of anaesthesia, the elders were moved to tears.Some of the elders went mute after watching the video, their heads buried in their hands as others covered their eyes with their face masks.